!!!5
%html
  %head
    %title Thomas Rix / rixth - San Franciscan software developer
    %meta{:name => 'description', :content => 'The personal page of Thomas Rix, a Kiwi software engineer living in San Francisco.'}
    %link{:href => 'style.css', :type => 'text/css', :rel => 'stylesheet'}
    %meta{:name => 'viewport', :content => 'width=device-width; initial-scale=1.0; maximum-scale=1.0; user-scalable=0;'}
  %body
    #wrapper
      #header
        %h1
          %a{href: "/"} Thomas Rix
      #main
        :markdown
          This marks my official home on the Internet. You can email me at [tom@rixth.org](mailto:tom@rixth.org).

          I currently [work](http://www.linkedin.com/in/tomrix) as a front end software engineer in the Bay Area. I am not currently seeking other opportunities. I also cycle, read, cook, [code](http://github.com/rixth), [photograph](http://www.flickr.com/photos/79329007@N00/), [listen](http://last.fm/user/rixth) &amp; rawk.
        %h2 Selected code
        %dl
          - @git.each do |repo|
            %dt
              %a{:href => repo['homepage'] != '' ? repo['homepage'] : repo['html_url']}= repo['name']
              %span
                = "#{repo['watchers']} watchers"
            %dd&= repo['description']
          %dt
            %a{:href => 'https://github.com/rixth/rixth.org'} rixth.org
            %span -1 watchers
          %dd The code that runs this website!
